# Frontend — Web Universe

The frontend project lives at **web-universe/** (Git submodule): Next.js, Marketplace, TypeScript SDK

## Structure (inside web-universe/)

- **apps/web/** — Next.js 14, App Router (main website)
- **apps/marketplace/** — Vite + React (marketplace)
- **packages/sdk/** — TypeScript SDK (@axionax/sdk) — put business logic here, not in apps

## Do

- Use **pnpm** (workspaces); do not use npm/yarn at the web-universe root
- **Imports:** use workspace aliases e.g. `import { ... } from "@axionax/sdk"` — never use relative paths across packages (e.g. ../../packages/sdk)
- **Next.js:** use Server Components by default; add `"use client"` only when using hooks (useState, useEffect)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS; Cyberpunk/Futuristic theme, dark mode by default

## Don't

- Don't put reusable logic in apps/web or apps/marketplace — move it to **packages/sdk**
- Don't hardcode API keys or secrets in frontend; use env (NEXT_PUBLIC_* for client)
